'''哈德鲁特''' ({{lang-hy|Հադրութ}})是[[阿塞拜疆|阿塞拜疆]][[霍賈文德區|霍賈文德區]]的一個鎮。1989年時該鎮人口[[亚美尼亚人|亚美尼亚人]]占多数。亚美尼亚人在此居住至[[2020年纳戈尔诺-卡拉巴赫战争|2020年纳戈尔诺-卡拉巴赫战争]]爆發<ref>{{cite web |url=https://drugoivzgliad.com/karabach-mir-i-voina-a-zubov/ |title=Андрей Зубов. Карабах: Мир и Война |author=Андрей Зубов |date= |website=drugoivzgliad.com |publisher= |access-date= |quote= |archive-date=2021-01-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210110205442/https://drugoivzgliad.com/karabach-mir-i-voina-a-zubov/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

在[[苏联|苏联]]时期，哈德鲁特为[[阿塞拜疆苏维埃社会主义共和国|阿塞拜疆苏维埃社会主义共和国]][[納戈爾諾－卡拉巴赫自治州|納戈爾諾－卡拉巴赫自治州]][[哈德鲁特区_(纳卡州)|哈德鲁特区]]的行政中心。第一次[[纳戈尔诺-卡拉巴赫战争|纳戈尔诺-卡拉巴赫战争]]后，哈德鲁特成为[[阿尔察赫共和国|阿尔察赫共和国]]{{link-en|哈德鲁特省|Hadrut Province}}的一部分。

在[[2020年納戈爾諾-卡拉巴赫戰爭|2020年納戈爾諾-卡拉巴赫戰爭]]期间<ref>{{Cite web|date=2020-10-23|title=Azerbaijan: Cluster Munitions Used in Nagorno-Karabakh|url=https://www.hrw.org/news/2020/10/23/azerbaijan-cluster-munitions-used-nagorno-karabakh|access-date=2020-11-22|website=Human Rights Watch|language=en|archive-date=2020-10-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201023084426/https://www.hrw.org/news/2020/10/23/azerbaijan-cluster-munitions-used-nagorno-karabakh|dead-url=no}}</ref>，阿塞拜疆军队大約于2020年10月9日占领了哈德鲁特<ref name="hadrutazerbaijan">{{Cite news |url=https://apa.az/en/nagorno_garabagh/President-of-Azerbaijan:-%22Hadrut-settlement-and-several-villages-liberated-from-occupation%22-332509 |title=President of Azerbaijan: 'Hadrut settlement and several villages liberated from occupation' |website=APA.az |access-date=2020-10-09 |date=2020-10-09 |language=en |quote=Azerbaijan's Hadrut settlement and several villages were liberated from Armenian aggressors, President Ilham Aliyev said this in his address to the nation, APA reports. |archive-date=2020-10-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201010123613/https://apa.az/en/nagorno_garabagh/President-of-Azerbaijan:-%22Hadrut-settlement-and-several-villages-liberated-from-occupation%22-332509 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|date=2020-10-19|title=Azerbaijani MoD shows soldiers who liberated Hadrut from Armenian occupation (PHOTO)|url=https://en.trend.az/azerbaijan/karabakh/3319598.html|access-date=2020-11-14|website=Trend.Az|language=en|archive-date=2020-11-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201127094959/https://en.trend.az/azerbaijan/karabakh/3319598.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。该镇在被占领后遭到阿塞拜疆士兵的破坏和抢劫。该镇教堂內的亚美尼亚人墓地也遭到破坏，墓碑被踢倒和砸碎<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.pbs.org/newshour/show/uneasy-peace-takes-hold-in-contested-region-of-azerbaijan |title=PBS NewsHour - Uneasy peace takes hold in contested region of Azerbaijan |accessdate=2020-12-13 |archive-date=2020-12-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201224144453/https://www.pbs.org/newshour/show/uneasy-peace-takes-hold-in-contested-region-of-azerbaijan |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

